1. sonarcube部署流程：
(1) run sonar in docker 
(2) login in
(3) generate token
user: austin
token: 1e3109f2795885dd70d1c2c65472fc7a73d0b693

sonar-scanner \
  -Dsonar.projectKey=first-test \
  -Dsonar.sources=. \
  -Dsonar.host.url=http://10.10.1.101:19099 \
  -Dsonar.login=1e3109f2795885dd70d1c2c65472fc7a73d0b693
  
reference:
https://www.cnblogs.com/longronglang/p/12845654.html
https://docs.sonarqube.org/latest/analysis/scan/sonarscanner/


2. plugins install
(1) 下载插件并将其拷贝进容器
docker cp checkstyle-sonar-plugin-8.40.jar sonarqube_sonarqube_1:/opt/sonarqube/extensions/plugins
(2) restart service 
operate in web gui
Administration--> System--> Restart Server

newest Checkstyle plugin checkstyle-sonar-plugin-8.40.jar requres SonarQube 7.9 version 以上版本
ERROR web[][o.s.s.p.Platform] Web server startup failed: Plugin Checkstyle [checkstyle] requires at least SonarQube 7.9
4.35版本的checkstyle也需要7.9以上


